&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a driven Account Executive with a proven track record of generating their own pipeline and closing six-figure SaaS/PaaS deals. This is a hunter role for someone who can identify opportunities, build senior relationships, and manage complex sales cycles from prospecting to close.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Main tasks and responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
